38 (1) "Adequate security measures" shall have the same meaning as the
39 term is means the same as defined in K.S.A. 75-7c20, and amendments
40 thereto;
41 (2) "possession" means having joint or exclusive control over a
42 firearm or having a firearm in a place where the person has some measure
43 of access and right of control; and

